data.description: This house is simply amazing! It is so clean and well-maintained; it has the appearance that it is not lived in. As soon as you enter through the front door, you will be greeted by a spacious and open floor plan that is sure to impress you. The kitchen boasts a stunning view of both the family room and living room, making it perfect for entertainment. The kitchen, dining area, powder room, and laundry room were all installed with new tile floors in 2023. On the second level, you will find a large media room that is perfect for movie nights. The master bath was also fitted with new tile floors in 2023, and the master bedroom is spacious and filled with natural light. All the secondary bedrooms are comfortable and cozy. The HVAC system is less than one year old, and the roof is less than two years old, so you can rest assured that the house is in great condition. Additionally, the community offers a huge swimming-tennis area that is perfect for family fun.
